E. L. CORD et al. v. Maynard McFIE, Receiver of Auburn-Fuller Co. No. 7301. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. July 10, 1934. Garnet C. Rainey, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellants. Chandler, Wright & Ward and John F. Gilbert, all of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, SAWTELLE, and GARRECHT, Circuit Judges.

*1003PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
